# Documentation

- Language: Vietnamese for `docs/` content
- Index: `docs/README.md` — keep navigation tables updated
- Source comments: English

## When changing code, update

| Change | Docs |
|--------|------|
| Public API | `docs/api-reference.md` |
| Input method rules | `docs/input-methods.md` |
| Architecture | `docs/architecture.md` |
| Any release | `docs/changelog.md` (`[Unreleased]` section) |

## Do not recreate root docs

All documentation belongs in `docs/`. Root `README.md` is a minimal pointer only.

## GitHub templates

Issue/PR templates live in `docs/github/`. Update there if template content changes.

## Full maintenance

For audit of entire `docs/` folder, use skill `maintain-docs` (see `audit-checklist.md`).
For single-feature updates, use `sync-feature-docs`.
